Feature Request/Bug Report

To report bugs or request new features of ShinyCardinal, please send an email to:

Dr.Yonghui Dong or Dr.Uwe Heinig

Cardinal Support

R package Cardinal includes a walkthrough vignette that showcases both its fundamental and advanced features. To learn more about Cardinal, please read here and here.

If you need any help, please visit Cardinal google help group.

Please Cite

If you use ShinyCardinal, please cite the following references:

1. Dong.Y., and Heinig, W., 2024. Mass Spectrometry Imaging Data Analysis with ShinyCardinal.

2. Bemis, K.A., Foell, M.C., Guo, D., Lakkimsetty, S.S., and Vitek, O., 2023. Cardinal v.3: a versatile open-source software for mass spectrometry imaging analysis. Nature Methods, 20, 1883-1886.
